OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to verbally abusing
OL,4,Cmultiple women and girls
OL,6,FA man who verbally abused multiple
OL,7,Fwomen and girls has pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Ffour public order offences during a
OL,9,Fhearing at Lincoln Magistrates' Court.
OL,11,FPaul Coleman, 62, of Millers Road in
OL,12,FWaddington, caused significant
OL,13,Fdistress to members of the public
OL,14,Facross a number of separate incidents
OL,15,Fduring the month of October,
OL,16,FLincolnshire Police said.
OL,18,FAll of the offences took place in the
OL,19,FWaddington area and were described by
OL,20,Fpolice as "completely unprovoked".
